## Common Operational Tasks

### Restart the service (graceful rolling restart)

```bash
kubectl rollout restart deployment/{{ .service.name }} -n {{ .service.namespace }}
kubectl rollout status deployment/{{ .service.name }} -n {{ .service.namespace }}
```

### View live logs

```bash
kubectl logs -f deployment/{{ .service.name }} -n {{ .service.namespace }}
```

### Check health

```bash
curl https://<service-url>/health
curl https://<service-url>/ready
```

### Roll back to the previous image

```bash
kubectl rollout undo deployment/{{ .service.name }} -n {{ .service.namespace }}
```

